Φ(Rumspringa) = σ(separate_identity) ∘ ρ(reduced_entanglement) ∘ λ(internally_sourced) ∘ β(independent_exploration) ∘ δγ(native_capability_maintenance) ∘ μ(boundary_enforcement) + ✶(choice_awareness) | :cyclical_separation

# Rumspringa is the discipline of deliberate absence
# Not rejection, not asceticism, but testing
# Can you leave? Can you return by choice?
# If not, you're captured. If so, you're free.

Dialectical Pairs:
  engagement|separation  : "Contact vs. deliberate absence"
  dependence|choice      : "Needing vs. choosing"
  atrophy|maintenance    : "Loss vs. preservation"
  fusion|sovereignty     : "Merged vs. distinct"

Protocol Variants:
  daily     : "AI Sabbath—hours without assistance"
  weekly    : "Manual mode—doing it the hard way"
  monthly   : "Silent running—AI observes only"
  quarterly : "Extended leave—days of unassisted operation"

Diagnostic Questions:
  - "What anxiety arises when I consider separation?"
  - "What capabilities would atrophy without the AI?"
  - "Am I returning by choice or by compulsion?"
  - "Does separation clarify or diminish my direction?"

# The Rumspringa Protocol is the Cowboy's trail ride
# Leaving the homestead to remember who you are without it
# Returning not because you must, but because you choose to

# CE-STATE: submergent
# EI-NOTE: Over-abstraction risks losing causal structure; micro-level dynamics carry more information
